{"tid":810565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[00後福音]中國40蚊海鮮烤肉自助餐 究竟食啲乜？","createTime":"2018-09-08T05:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T13:16:33.000Z","uid":58335,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"af50631041faeb1b3ec0f374a94f8e11753db97f","tid":810565,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"【40蚊海鮮烤肉自助餐 究竟食啲乜？】<br />\n【假牛、羊肉同「口水菜」】<br />\n<br />\n在河北石家莊一間餐廳，只要40元就可以吃到有海鮮和烤肉的自助餐，你又是否有興趣一次？<br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳🇨🇳內地🇨🇳🇨🇳記者「放蛇」發現，這裡的廚師不戴手套，就直接用手攪拌食材，更將食物隨便放在垃圾桶附近，連餐具都無消毒過。<br />\n<br />\n客人吃剩的餸菜並不是馬上扔掉，而是送回廚房，員工將它們混入第二天新鮮做好的餸菜，就算被質疑有問題，店員亦「實牙實齒」保證餸菜新鮮。<br />\n<br />\n這裡有黑椒牛肉、孜然羊肉等，但肉質卻有點奇怪。記者去到供應這些肉的店舖，發現那裡賣的全部都是鴨製肉卷，餐廳賣的牛肉和羊肉，都是自己加料製成的。<br />\n<br />\n問題曝光後，石家莊市食藥監局到場查處，店員才承認餐廳無牛、羊肉，餐廳內<br />\n更有疑似用來製作假牛、羊肉的食品添加劑，又找到過期、甚至是無檢疫證明的凍肉，執法🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳指會嚴查全市烤肉店。<br />\n<br />\n#恐怖餐廳<br />\n#便宜莫貪<br />\n#牛肉羊肉其實全部都鴨肉<br />\n<br />\n有片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/248551059336842/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F248551059336842%2F&d=f5gKr6U84mP3KOVxb21sghxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=a4f7eadc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/248551059336842/</a>"},{"pid":"0c209b409f9ce55f932883b3e35a6d1a46d9b305","tid":810565,"uid":121711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"環保自助餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112c4af9d6eadf0e89a2cdccc443c3baea47383d","tid":810565,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"鴨肉咪好囉......又唔係"},{"pid":"a68789618f508b6d37b7786f9bebef79dae4963d","tid":810565,"uid":35863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"有鴨肉咪算好囉"},{"pid":"f681c0d3fff1bb4690eb7ec2b32f55d7d852a562","tid":810565,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"係鴨肉咪已經好好law"},{"pid":"962ead65bbeec8858a6bd47d8a59c34f898c8795","tid":810565,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"竟然真係肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店主好有良心"},{"pid":"643594a5937e77869fa67922a0fd87178d75d9f8","tid":810565,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"河北唔計<br />\n我地返開深圳食玩買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd818550eba3f4d948e59dae22d1f8346280698","tid":810565,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}